HEADWORD: Interfacial
<hw>In`ter*fa"cial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Included between two plane surfaces or faces; <as>as,
